      • runAction

        protected void runAction(java.lang.String name,
             java.lang.Runnable r)
        Disables the action components, starts a new Thread and executes the given Runnable.

        After the Runnable finished it re-enables the action components.

        An Thread.UncaughtExceptionHandler will print name + " fehlgeschlagen." and delegate the exception to PrimesApplication.error(Throwable, Thread, boolean).
